{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SVi3hGzYmCHRYjVrkNRVw3","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Implementation History — 004-shared-infrastructure\n     2→\n     3→Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4→attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5→of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Iteration 1 — lifecycle.rs\n    10→\n    11→Created `solana/shared/src/lifecycle.rs` with:\n    12→- `RoundPhase` enum (6 variants) with Anchor serialization derives\n    13→- `transition(current, target) -> Result<()>` validating 9 allowed transitions, rejecting all others\n    14→- `RoundTimestamps` struct with `created_at`, `locked_at`, `resolve_deadline`, `settled_at`\n    15→- `LifecycleError::InvalidTransition` error code\n    16→- 3 unit tests: valid transitions, invalid transitions (including LOCKED→SETTLED), enum serialization roundtrip\n    17→\n    18→Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `lifecycle` module.\n    19→\n    20→**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` — 7 tests passed (4 existing + 3 new).\n    21→\n    22→## Iteration 1 — 2026-02-25T21:35:21Z — OK\n    23→- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n    24→\n    25→## Iteration 2 — timeout.rs\n    26→\n    27→Created `solana/shared/src/timeout.rs` with:\n    28→- `DEFAULT_RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS: i64 = 120` constant\n    29→- `TimeoutError::ResolveDeadlineExceeded` error code\n    30→- `is_expired(resolve_deadline, now) -> bool` — returns true when `now >= resolve_deadline`\n    31→- `enforce_not_expired(resolve_deadline, now) -> Result<()>` — returns error if expired\n    32→- 6 unit tests: boundary conditions (exactly at deadline, 1 second before, 1 second after) for both functions\n    33→\n    34→Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `timeout` module. Existing `LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS` in `constants.rs` preserved.\n    35→\n    36→**Verification**: `cargo test -p r